Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Iwama, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel great. Well done, Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a bit, so watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What network should I play in today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope there are some cute girls there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You, hiding over there, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You found me so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from Iwama Mitsune-san,\NCEO of the Saishisumu Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you connect from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get into my network?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for forcing my way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to ask you for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This network is incredibly well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spied on many networks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the first time I've seen something\Nso complete and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This network would serve perfectly\Nas a pipeline to the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me build a gate here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what this was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take me for an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this network.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't sell it, no matter\Nhow much you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's that about a Demon Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That I cannot tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess we can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop blabbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How very human to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Iwama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a system error.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave now, I don't mind\Nletting you off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out of my network!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your network?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, now it's my network.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I just tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Adams, delete the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Erase the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should hurry and run away before\Nyour network disappears completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Adams, bring me back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give up, Miss Mitsune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you allow me to build the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking to do it free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, I'll give you\Nthe greatest pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you always do the\Nsame thing to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sto–
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I had so much\Ntrouble with that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have called me,\Nsince you're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to come out on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening the seal by yourself\Nis a breach of contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I don't remember making\Na contract with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My master is and always\Nwill be Kaname-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for you, Mitsurugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your master right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He told me to listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At least for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You only call us when you're\Nfacing a weak enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever it actually gets dangerous,\Nyou always do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone getting in my\Nway when I'm fighting seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would happen if you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You were seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body isn't yours alone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you get injured,\NKaname-sama also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Mitsurugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can really run your mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're lagging behind down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So rough... I'll break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! This is too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have my own way of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect Kaname-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There will definitely come a time\Nwhen I'll rely on all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All you girls have to do is believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll believe in you. And so will the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha–
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You two! When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They came out of their seals\Nat the same time I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. Our master always needs\Nto have everything his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I'll try my hardest from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trying your hardest" is\Nmeaningless in your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should start off by\Nlearning how to assist us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I can only\Npull half my weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,More like a quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back into your seals already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you this much.\NThere's no point in just killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, demons of her level have\Nbecome much more numerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the rumor that\Nthe gate's been opened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that demons have\Nrecently been appearing often.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're all in such a small area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if they're being\Ndrawn in by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Acid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you this much:\NThere's no point in just killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this is all leading up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna cum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,More, please. Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop. I want more, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you grant me that favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, this pleasure will be\Nyours for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. I'll do anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll open the gate to the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the gate has opened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsurugi, this is how I do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You damned fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, have you noticed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate has been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are about to get nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How many centuries has it been\Nsince you became my master?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And all this time, you haven't grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had the choice\Nof ending your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've kept sealing demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can step down once the\Nnext master appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Mitsurugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission is to seal demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we kill them, the balance with the\NDemon Realm will be disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Both worlds will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle that is about to begin\Nwill be beyond vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori and the others are with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so are you, Mitsurugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I fight alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight, Mitsurugi, as all the\Nmasters before me have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the gate has opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:23:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should seal it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy! Don't make it sound so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't help but fight\Nwhenever you see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As Kusuka said, the first\Nchallenge is finding the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't allow demons to get any\Ncloser to people than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.20,0:24:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsurugi and I will give it our all,\Nso lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We will, Kaname-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.60,0:24:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.60,0:24:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.40,0:24:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,344)\c&H2A0B82&}Damon Hunters
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.40,0:24:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}aoi hikari hashirinuke
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrun the blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hametsu no tobira hiraku toki
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when the gates of destruction open
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.52,0:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hikari no honoo kanashimi no kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.52,0:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A flame of light, a wind of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.68,0:25:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}dareka ga kimi wo yondeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.68,0:25:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is calling you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou zankan yobisamase mune no oku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zankan! Awaken in the depths of your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou zankan dokiharae mugen no chikara wo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zankan! Wield your limitless power
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:26:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}harukana jikai wa toki wo koe
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:26:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A far-off meeting surpasses time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.96,0:26:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}in no kagayaki ga kakeru keru
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.96,0:26:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The brilliance is missing from the shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yami wo kirisake muteki no yaiba Mitsurugi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierce through the darkness, invincible blade Mitsurugi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.16,0:26:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kuroki arashi fukiarete
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.16,0:26:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A black wind blows violently
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hijou no sadame semaru toki
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as the appointed time draws near
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.72,0:26:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}inochi wo iyasu daichi no inori
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.72,0:26:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The foremost prayer is to spare life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.04,0:26:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}dareka ga kimi wo motomete iru
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.04,0:26:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is seeking you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou zankan tachiagare yuuki wo daite
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Zankan! Stand up, and embrace courage
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.40,0:27:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou zankan sora wo kake imawashii uwa donaru
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.40,0:27:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zankan! Fly in the sky, and shout obscenely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mesameyou tamashii toki wo koe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Surpass time, awakened soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.12,0:27:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ashita no kidou mamoru tame
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.12,0:27:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect the path tomorrow takes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.80,0:27:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yami ni kirameku seigi no yaiba Mitsurugi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.80,0:27:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The justice that shines in the darkness,\Ninvincible blade Mitsurugi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.92,0:27:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou zankan yobisamase mune no oku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.92,0:27:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zankan! Awaken in the depths of your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou zankan dokiharae mugen no chikara wo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zankan! Wield your limitless power
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.88,0:28:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}harukana jikai wa toki wo koe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.88,0:28:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A far-off meeting surpasses time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}in no kagayaki ga kakeru keru
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The brilliance is missing from the shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.76,0:28:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yami wo kirisake muteki no yaiba Mitsurugi
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.76,0:28:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierce through the darkness, invincible blade Mitsurugi
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.48,0:28:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.28,0:28:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.16,0:28:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.60,0:28:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had the feeling that\Nsomething was approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:28:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is it something scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.36,0:29:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.20,0:29:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now calm down and continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.40,0:29:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.60,0:29:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.12,0:29:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my precious link\Nconnected to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay like that a little longer.
